tags.wheelchair:description: Accessible from carpark via a ramped escalator and a lift. Automatic sliding doors at entrances/exits. Width of aisles and self serve checkout heights are appropriate. High shelves can't be accessed independently in wheelchair.

Coles Local
tags.wheelchair:description: Narrow aisles. Products shelves are too high. Difficulty opening door of refrigerator as it needs be manually pulled open. No wheel-in space at self check-out and cashier counters. Difficulty communicating with staff over high meat counters.
